name: The Sun
description:
"The Sun card represents success, happiness, abundance, and radiance. Like the sun itself, it gives strength and vitality to all those that are lucky enough to feel its rays. There is much joy and happiness that is coming to you.

Because of your own personal fulfillment, you provide others with inspiration and joy as well. People are drawn to you because they are capable of seeing the warm and beautiful energy which you bring into their lives." 

I've always thought of you as the sun card. Not just because you brought a lot of happiness and pure joy into my life, but because you're also a little ray of sunshine yourself. 

Here's to you radiating and living your best life at 27 <3 

Happiest birthday Kenzo <3 <3
